						</tr>
						<tr>
							<td><strong>Preamble</strong></td>
							<td>WHEREAS it is expedient to amend the law for regulating inquiries into the behaviour of public servants not removable from their appointments without the sanction of the Government, and to make the same uniform throughout 1[ Bangladesh]; It is enacted as follows:-</td>
